examples.en: Upend the box and empty the contents.
I upended the bucket to use as a stool.
He upended his opponent with a single punch.
He upended the bicycle to fix its flat tire.
He upended the box and emptied the contents.
The boys used to pretend to be upending the bottle and hiccup.
The security inspector upended my bag and dumped everything out.
A giant wave upended the surfers.
